mesa
------------------------------------------
X11 OpenGL libraries

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.7-1
  libgcc1-4.5.0-1
  libstdc++6-4.5.0-1
  libX11-xcb1-1.3.5-1
  libX11_6-1.3.5-1
  libxcb-glx0-1.7-1
  libxcb1-1.6-1
  libXext6-1.1.2-1
  libXm2-0.95.2-2
  libXt6-1.0.8-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  binutils-2.20.51-2
  cygport-0.10.0-1
  gcc4-core-4.5.0-1
  gcc4-g++-4.5.0-1
  make-3.81-2
  pkg-config-0.23b-10
  sed-4.2.1-1
  glproto-1.4.12-1

Canonical website:
  http://mesa3d.org/

Canonical download:
  ftp://ftp.freedesktop.org/pub/mesa/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack mesa-7.8.2-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./mesa-7.8.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mesa-7.8.2-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/mesa-7.8.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGL-devel-7.8.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGL1-7.8.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLU-devel-7.8.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLU1-7.8.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLw-devel-7.8.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLw1-7.8.2-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

